SELECT NAME, SUM(AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM USERS U LEFT OUTER JOIN TRANSACTIONS T ON U.ACCOUNT = T.ACCOUNT GROUP BY NAME HAVING SUM(AMOUNT) > 10000
WITH TMP AS ( SELECT ACCOUNT, SUM(AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM TRANSACTIONS GROUP BY ACCOUNT HAVING SUM(AMOUNT) > 10000 ) SELECT U.NAME, TMP.BALANCE FROM USERS U JOIN TMP ON U.ACCOUNT = TMP.ACCOUNT
SELECT NAME, SUM(T.AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM USERS AS U LEFT JOIN TRANSACTIONS AS T ON U.ACCOUNT = T.ACCOUNT GROUP BY U.ACCOUNT HAVING SUM(T.AMOUNT) > 10000
SELECT USERS.NAME, SUM(TRANSACTIONS.AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM TRANSACTIONS LEFT JOIN USERS ON USERS.ACCOUNT=TRANSACTIONS.ACCOUNT GROUP BY TRANSACTIONS.ACCOUNT HAVING SUM(TRANSACTIONS.AMOUNT)>10000
SELECT NAME, SUM(AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM TRANSACTIONS T JOIN USERS USING(ACCOUNT) GROUP BY ACCOUNT HAVING SUM(AMOUNT)>10000
SELECT USERS.NAME, TRANS.BALANCE FROM USERS JOIN (SELECT SUM(AMOUNT) AS BALANCE, ACCOUNT FROM TRANSACTIONS GROUP BY ACCOUNT ) AS TRANS ON TRANS.ACCOUNT = USERS.ACCOUNT WHERE TRANS.BALANCE > 10000
SELECT NAME AS NAME,SUM(AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM USERS LEFT JOIN TRANSACTIONS ON USERS.ACCOUNT= TRANSACTIONS.ACCOUNT GROUP BY USERS.ACCOUNT HAVING SUM(AMOUNT)>10000
SELECT U.NAME, SUM(T.AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM TRANSACTIONS T INNER JOIN USERS U ON U.ACCOUNT=T.ACCOUNT GROUP BY T.ACCOUNT HAVING BALANCE>10000
SELECT U.NAME, SUM(T.AMOUNT) AS BALANCE FROM USERS U, TRANSACTIONS T WHERE U.ACCOUNT = T.ACCOUNT GROUP BY U.NAME HAVING SUM(AMOUNT) >10000
